     <statement>
        <p> 
        When we are talking about slope, students from American schools often say the words “rise” and “run.” Explain in your own words what “rise” and “run” mean. How do we combine “rise” and “run” to determine slope?
        </p>
        </statement> 
         <response />
    </exercise> 

